<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>If i do this:</p>

<p>$a=new Zend_Date();
$b=clone $a;</p>

<p>and this:
$a-&gt;isLater($b,'yyyy-MM-dd')</p>

<p>I should get a false value, insted I get a TRUE value.</p>

<p>If i use:
$a-&gt;isLater($b,Zend_Date::DATES)</p>

<p>I get the correct value (false).</p>

